metadata.name: KAMUY-HKD PASS #1
metadata.description:
Hokkaido,Japan, where exclusive food treasures are  produced in the world.

 Ingredients from Hokkaido are among the highest quality in the world.

 We wish people around the world to enjoy Hokkaido's exclusive ingredients,

 which are rarely distributed in the market.

 In addition to providing special ingredients, we partner with

 restaurants and chefs around the world to offer

 menus and events exclusive to NFT holders.

  Events will be held not only in Hokkaido,

 But also in New York, Paris, and other cities around the world.

 And we invite you to visit Hokkaido and enjoy the delights and nature.

 A portion of the proceeds is to be returned to the community to protect the ingredients and nature of Hokkaido.
